SUMMARY:The Doorway
DESCRIPTION:Three chapters. Three rooms. One child recalling his memories. \nThe Doorway is a solo performance in which one body brings four characters to life: a father\, a brother\, a mother\, and a dog. Director and performer Yash draws on his personal experiences to create a world where objects come to life. Through old photographs\, puppetry\, narration\, and live performance\, the audience pieces together a rather honest family portrait.  \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/the-doorway/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Performing Arts,Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Thumbnail-12.jpg
END:VEVENT
